channel.title: Need Help [PI]
channel.description: How do i make a webclient? i am trying to make a webclient on rswebclients.com but its not working... when i go to load the webclient it goes to a google page that says like "oops we cant find what your looking for" so is there any way i can make a webclient? is there any other websites?

item.title: Need Help [PI]
item.dc:creator: @voetbal645 voetbal645
item.description:
@voetbal645 wrote:

Make your own web client, there are enough tutorials to do it.
Look the tutorial section. In the project insanity bases is the client almost web client ready, the only thing that you need to do is.
Zipping the cache correctly,
Changing the Cache name and in signlink.java to,
Upload the zipped cache to your public folder of dropbox,
Change the cache link in cachedownloader.java,
And then jar the client and upload to a web host with html
